<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">匿名用户</h3></div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="42">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wang-min-39" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wang-min-39" class="zg-link" title="王敏">王敏</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$wu-de-50" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/wu-de-50" class="zg-link" title="伍德">伍德</a></span>
